20#ifndef __CACHE_H
21#define __CACHE_H
22
23#include <freerdp/api.h>
24#include <freerdp/types.h>
25#include <freerdp/update.h>
26#include <freerdp/utils/stream.h>
27
28#include <freerdp/cache/glyph.h>
29#include <freerdp/cache/brush.h>
30#include <freerdp/cache/pointer.h>
31#include <freerdp/cache/bitmap.h>

34
35struct rdp_cache
36{
37 rdpGlyphCache* glyph; /* 0 */
38 rdpBrushCache* brush; /* 1 */
39 rdpPointerCache* pointer; /* 2 */
40 rdpBitmapCache* bitmap; /* 3 */
41 rdpOffscreenCache* offscreen; /* 4 */
42 rdpPaletteCache* palette; /* 5 */
43
44 /* internal */
45
46 rdpSettings* settings;
47};
48
49FREERDP_API rdpCache* cache_new(rdpSettings* settings);
50FREERDP_API void cache_free(rdpCache* cache);

52#endif /* __CACHE_H */
